'''2008年苏里南空难'''发生于该年4月3日，一家[[苏里南蓝翼航空|苏里南蓝翼航空]]的安-28（[[航空器注册编号|注册编号]] PZ-TSO<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dbsuriname.com/archief/nat/2008/apr08/04-04-08/Nat_Negentien%20doden%20bij%20ongeluk%20met%20toestel%20Blue%20Wing%20.asp |title=Negentien doden bij ongeluk met toestel Blue Wing |date=2008-04-04 |accessdate=2008-04-04 |publisher=''[[Dagblad_Suriname|Dagblad Suriname]]'' |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080906160510/http://www.dbsuriname.com/archief/nat/2008/apr08/04-04-08/Nat_Negentien%20doden%20bij%20ongeluk%20met%20toestel%20Blue%20Wing%20.asp |archivedate=2008-09-06 }}</ref>
）在[[苏里南|苏里南]][[Benzdorp|Benzdorp]]的[[拉瓦·安提诺机场|拉瓦·安提诺机场]]降落时坠毁。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7329392.stm |title=Plane crashes in southern Surinam |date=2008-04-03 |accessdate=2008-04-04 |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |archive-date=2008-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080407193747/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7329392.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nu.nl/news/1510126/20/Twintig_doden_door_vliegtuigramp_Suriname.html |title=Twintig doden door vliegtuigramp Suriname |date=2008-04-03 |accessdate=2008-04-04 |publisher=Nu.nl |language=nl |archive-date=2008-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080404154330/http://www.nu.nl/news/1510126/20/Twintig_doden_door_vliegtuigramp_Suriname.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 
机上的17名乘客和2名机组成员全部罹难。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.trouw.nl/hetnieuws/wereld/article957455.ece/Vliegramp_in_Suriname_negentien_doden |title=Vliegramp in Suriname: negentien doden |date=2008-04-03 |accessdate=2008-04-04 |publisher=''[[Trouw|Trouw]]'' |language=nl |archive-date=2008-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430005759/http://www.trouw.nl/hetnieuws/wereld/article957455.ece/Vliegramp_in_Suriname_negentien_doden |dead-url=no }}</ref>

事故大约发生在当地时间11:00（[[UTC-3|西三区]]，14:00 [[UTC|UTC]]）。媒体最初报道为飞机因跑道上停有一家安-28而放弃降落。
<ref>{{Cite news |author=Ivan Cairo |url=http://www.caribbeannetnews.com/news-6978--36-36--.html |title=Twenty feared dead in Suriname plane crash |publisher=Caribbean Net News |date=2008-04-03 |accessdate=2008-04-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080526032159/http://www.caribbeannetnews.com/news-6978--36-36--.html |archivedate=2008-05-26 }}</ref>
在复飞时因未达到足够的高度撞毁在附近的山上。
<ref name="Radio 10">{{Cite news |url=http://radio10.sr/content/view/2657/ |title=Vliegtuigcrash in Lawa gebied. Alle 19 inzittenden om het leven gekomen |date=2008-04-03 |accessdate=2008-04-04 |publisher=[[Radio10|Radio10]] |language=nl |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725084308/http://radio10.sr/content/view/2657/ |archivedate=2011-07-25 }}</ref>
该班飞机在当地时间10:00于苏里南首都的[[佐格恩胡普机场|佐格恩胡普机场]]起飞，<ref>{{Cite news |title=Forensic teams head to site of Suriname plane crash |url=http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5jsrxO3F9MZERza9ZUUDCeTF1yTLg |publisher=Agence France Press |date=2008-04-05 |accessdate=2008-04-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520125449/http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5jsrxO3F9MZERza9ZUUDCeTF1yTLg |archivedate=2011-05-20 }}</ref>
机上的乘客都供职于苏里南一家名为[[Telesur|Telesur]]的[[电信公司|电信公司]]。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telesur.sr/website/nieuws.asp?id=285&menuid=25 |publisher=Telesur |date=2008-04-04 |accessdate=2008-04-04 |title=Met innige deelneming... |language=nl |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080422061504/http://www.telesur.sr/website/nieuws.asp?id=285&menuid=25 |archivedate=2008-04-22 }}</ref>

在事故当天举行的发布会上，[[苏里南总统|苏里南总统]][[罗纳德·费内希恩|罗纳德·费内希恩]]表示政府要尽力改善该国大量的简易机场以避免类似事故的发生。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2008-04/05/content_7921070.htm |language=zh-cn |title=19人被证实在苏里南空难中丧生 |publisher=新华网 |date=2008-04-05 |accessdate=2011-08-20 |archive-date=2008-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081010183634/http://news.xinhuanet.com/newscenter/2008-04/05/content_7921070.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==伤亡情况==
飞行员索里亚尼·乔乌-维尔奎尔（Soeriani Jhauw-Verkuijl）是蓝翼航空执行官阿米查德·乔乌（Amichand Jhauw）的妻子，她的兄弟和同事目睹了这场空难。<ref name="Radio 10"/>驾驶罗伯特·拉金来自Antecume Pata的一个六口之家，是法属圭亚那的公民。
<ref name="Novum0405">{{Cite news |url=http://www.elsevier.nl/nieuws/laatste_24_uur/artikel/asp/artnr/200311/ |title='Motoruitval oorzaak vliegramp Suriname' |date=2008-04-05 |accessdate=2008-04-07 |publisher=[[Novum|Novum]]/[[Elsevier|Elsevier]] |language=nl |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080412024345/http://www.elsevier.nl/nieuws/laatste_24_uur/artikel/asp/artnr/200311/ |archivedate=2008-04-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.caribbeannetnews.com/news-7022--36-36--.html |title=Authorities launch formal investigation into Suriname plane crash |date=2008-04-05 |author=Ivan Cairo |publisher=Caribbean Net News |accessdate=2008-04-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080606010734/http://www.caribbeannetnews.com/news-7022--36-36--.html |archivedate=2008-06-06 }}</ref>

[[荷兰国家警察|荷兰国家警察]]派出了一队法医来协助确认罹难者身份。
<ref>{{Cite news |title=Nederlands team op weg naar Suriname |url=http://www.trouw.nl/hetnieuws/nederland/article957766.ece/Nederlands_team_op_weg_naar_Suriname |publisher=[[Trouw|Trouw]] |date=2008-04-00 |accessdate=2008-04-04 |language=nl |archive-date=2019-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123184119/https://www.trouw.nl/hetnieuws/nederland/article957766.ece/Nederlands_team_op_weg_naar_Suriname |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nrc.nl/buitenland/article1037774.ece/Nederlandse_hulp_voor_Suriname_na_vliegramp |title=Nederlandse hulp voor Suriname na vliegramp |publisher=[[NRC_Handelsblad|NRC Handelsblad]] |date=2008-04-04 |accessdate=2008-04-04 |language=nl |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080407234717/http://www.nrc.nl/buitenland/article1037774.ece/Nederlandse_hulp_voor_Suriname_na_vliegramp |archive-date=2008-04-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
该机构通过检验DNA鉴定出其中九名遇难者是苏里南人，另外十名无法通过DNA确认。<ref>[http://www.nu.nl/algemeen/1565089/slachtoffers-surinaamse-vliegramp-geidentificeerd.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.nu.nl/algemeen/1565089/slachtoffers-surinaamse-vliegramp-geidentificeerd.html |date=20191014133807 }} [Suriname plane crash victims identified] ] 13 May 2008 (in Dutch)</ref>

